                    <p class="mt-4 border-t border-blue-100 pt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:border-blue-900/60 dark:text-slate-300">Bulk SMS is a service that lets businesses send large volumes of text messages to multiple recipients simultaneously. For Tamil Nadu businesses, it means you can reach customers in Chennai, Coimbatore, Madurai, Trichy, and all other districts instantly &mdash; for promotions, alerts, OTPs, or reminders &mdash; at a very low cost per message.</p>
