                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 border-t border-blue-100 pt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:border-blue-900/60 dark:text-slate-300"><strong>Promotional SMS</strong> is used for marketing campaigns &mdash; offers, discounts, and brand announcements. It can only be sent to Non-DND numbers between 9 AM and 9 PM. <strong>Transactional SMS</strong> is for critical communications like OTPs, payment confirmations, and order updates. It can be sent 24&times;7, including to DND-registered numbers.</p>
